                    <span>Great book!! Clear, easy and acurated text!! Great Methodology!! Simple and objective!!<P>A must have for anyone who needs manage and design unix data centers.<P>The only problem: This book needs a 2002 update release covering the newest Sun hardware and the most server intensive needs made by web-centric computing.</span>
                  
              
